;; cljfmt configuration shipped with the scaffolded project.
;;
;; The verification harness runs `cljfmt check src spec dev` and requires every
;; file to be formatted (exit 0).
;;
;; Only trailing-whitespace cleanup is enabled. The template source carries
;; scaffolder feature/db block markers that are stripped line-by-line, and uses
;; a closing-delimiter-on-own-line style inside require/feature blocks so those
;; blocks stay easy to add/remove. cljfmt's indentation reflow,
;; surrounding-whitespace removal, and blank-line collapsing would move
;; delimiters across marker boundaries and unbalance a form once a feature is
;; stripped. Restricting cljfmt to trailing-whitespace keeps the check
;; deterministic and strip-safe across every feature combination.
{:indentation?                    false
 :remove-surrounding-whitespace?  false
 :remove-trailing-whitespace?     true
 :insert-missing-whitespace?      false
 :remove-consecutive-blank-lines? false}
